ygData.msgSnippet: Then I think Verant needs to really do something about all this.  I mean if places like Unrest and Cazic are gonna be so over crowded that it cause so much lag
ygData.messageBody:
Then I think Verant needs to really do something about all this. I mean if
places like Unrest and Cazic are gonna be so over crowded that it cause so
much lag then maybe they should hurry up and give as that new land mass they
been working on or something. But of course once we get this on land mass
you know it'll be crowded for a long time, everyone will be dying to go see
what it's like.

**************************
Azor
Lvl 16 Human Cleric of the Rathe
